source: instance_bill and ProductCode:batchcompute | select case when rnk1 =1 then Region else '' end as Region , case when rnk2 = 1 then class else '' end  as "费用类型",BillingItem as "计费项", concat(cast( round(Usage,3) as varchar),' (' , UsageUnit,')') as"用量", "费用",concat(cast(round(feepercent,3) as varchar) ,'%') as "同比上月" from(  select *, sum("费用") over(partition by Region) as regionFee,sum("费用") over(partition by Region,class) as RegionClassFee , rank() over(partition by Region order by "费用" desc) as rnk1,rank() over(partition by Region, class order by "费用" desc) as rnk2  from ( 
select region,class, billingitem, usagediff[1] as Usage, usagediff[3]*100-100 as UsagePercent, usageunit, feediff[1] as "费用", feediff[3]*100-100 as feePercent from(
select region,class, billingitem, compare(usage,2592000) as usagediff, arbitrary(usageUnit) as usageunit, compare("费用",2592000) as feediff from(
select Region ,split_part(split_part(InstanceID, ';',1), '-', 1) as class, BillingItem, sum(Usage) as usage, arbitrary(UsageUnit) as UsageUnit, round(sum(PretaxAmount),3) as "费用"  from log group by Region,class,BillingItem  ) group by region,class,billingitem
) 
) )order by regionFee desc, RegionClassFee desc ,"费用" desc  limit 1000
